Cursed Images - Memesplaining
Super Deluxe
June 7, 2018
https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=SsNBhWxUIb0 (5:04)
____________________________________________

In September of 2016, an account called @uncursedimages (https://twitter.com/uncursedimages/status/791824354359279616) was made. It began providing the backstory for as many accursed image posts as it could.

Daryl: For example, it traced this cursed image back to this episode of the web series Best of the Worst, in which one member of the cast is confronted with the original polaroid from his childhood.
